sudo su

1.Firewall: 
sudo apt update && sudo apt install ufw -y && sudo ufw allow from any && sudo ufw reload && sudo ufw status verbose && echo "y" | sudo ufw enable

2. Install by github: Debian 12, 13
sudo apt update && wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ysurac/openmptcprouter-vps/refs/heads/develop/debian9-x86_64.sh && chmod +x debian9-x86_64.sh && KERNEL="6.12" sudo ./debian9-x86_64.sh

3.Finish after installation "reboot" then ssh port chnaged to: 65222
!!! Keys are in /root/openmptcprouter_config.txt !!!

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

Error Fixes: after fix run step 2 again.
/etc/shadowsocks-libev/manager.json: No such file or directory â€” 

mkdir -p /etc/shadowsocks-libev && touch /etc/shadowsocks-libev/manager.json && systemctl restart omr-admin
